---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { url } from '../../utils'
import ArrowRight from '../ArrowRight.astro'
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container columns">
    <div class="column-a">
      <p class="topper">About</p>
      <h2 class="h2 heading has-underline">A Carer Who Truly Understands</h2>
      <p class="paragraph">
        I know that hollow feeling in your stomach when you need to find help
        for a loved one. Maybe you're an older person who hates asking for
        assistance, or a family member terrified of choosing the wrong carer. I
        understand completely - I felt the same while caring for my mum with
        dementia and my dad with cancer.
      </p>
      <p class="paragraph">
        Over 30 years as a registered childminder, I learned just how precious
        trust is when welcoming someone into your home. Now, I bring that same
        warmth, patience, and dedication to helping older adults stay
        independent—because life should be lived fully at every age and under
        their own terms.
      </p>
      <a href={url('/about/')} class="link">
        <span>Read More</span>
        <ArrowRight />
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="column-b">
      <div class="image-wrapper has-dots-before has-dots-after">
        <Image
          src={import('../../assets/images/hero-image-1.png')}
          alt="A senior lady smiling and talking with her companion."
          widths={[166, 344]}
          sizes="(max-width: 767px) 50vw, 25vw"
          class="image"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .columns {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .topper {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(var(--rgb-colour-text-base), 0.66);
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .paragraph {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--colour-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 300ms ease;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;

    &:hover {
      color: rgba(var(--rgb-colour-accent), 0.75);
    }

    &:active {
      color: rgba(var(--rgb-colour-accent), 0.5);
    }
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;

    &::after {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  .image {
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 11px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 22rem) {
    .image-wrapper {
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;

      &::after {
        display: initial;
      }
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 46rem) {
    .columns {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .column-b {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
      max-width: 20rem;
    }

    .image {
      aspect-ratio: 377/584;
      border-radius: 9999px;
    }
  }
</style>
